name: Angie Everhart
description:
Angela Kay Everhart is an American actress and former model who appeared in several Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issues in the 1990s and posed nude for Playboy in 2000.

Dabbling with some TI works, I wanted one of Angie using mostly images from the 90s I could find online since I enjoy that time in her career.
